name: Muhammad Zubair
tagline: Official Website of Muhammad Zubair (Co-Founder and CTO Datalide Technologies)
body: Welcome to my website. I am currently a CTO of Datalide which I Co-Founded With My Colleagues in Back 2019 during an attempt to reach Base Camp of Nanga Parbat. Our Goal was to develop Datalide in 2 years which we accomplished in less than a year.
